          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="star-icon"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="star-icon"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="star-icon"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="star-icon"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="body-md testimonial-text">
          "Managing medication schedules for my elderly parents was stressful. With Family Monitoring and Alerts, we never miss a dose. Absolutely a lifesaver."
        </p>
        <div class="testimonial-user">
          <div class="user-avatar-wrapper blue-grad">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="avatar-svg">
              <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="user-meta">
            <h4 class="user-name">Michael Vance</h4>
            <span class="user-role">Family Coordinator</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl) auto;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    display: block;
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-body);
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
  }

  .star-rating {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: #eab308; /* Yellow-500 */
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-body);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    flex-grow: 1;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .testimonial-user {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-canvas-soft-2);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .user-avatar-wrapper {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-level-2);
  }

  .avatar-svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .user-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .user-name {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .user-role {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-mute);
  }

  /* Responsive styles */
  @media (max-width: 959px) {
    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
